May be an image of text that says 'How to apply the SHIFT METHOD to unleash your TRUE POTENTIAL Step 1: See Figure out what it is that you want to do. What are your goals? Now, see the holes that are preventing you from reaching your goal. Remove distractions The key to becoming successful in what you do is to fall in love with taking action rather than treating reaching the destination as the only source of happiness. Find joy in doing your work. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How to apply the SHIFT METHOD to unleash your TRUE POTENTIAL Step 2: Shift Make a personalized Shift plan. Once you figure out what you have to work upon, starting working on it. Make those little movements in your life that will ultimately change the course of your life completely. Keep it simple. Do the stuff that you are supposed to do and not the things that others are doing. @awareness_of_success'.

Photo by Awareness • Mindset • Success on September 18, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How to apply the SHIFT METHOD to unleash your TRUE POTENTIAL Step 3: Sustain Sustainability is about having discipline in your life. In order to reach your goal, you will have to follow a routine. That IS the secret to keep doing something for a long time. Discipline yourself to keep up with your plan so that you reach your goals. Disciplineis a far better enabler than motivation. @awareness_of_success'.

We have Anthony Truck, former NFL player, coach, mentor, entrepreneur, speak to us this time around. 🏈

Anthony Trucks is a man who has forged his life with fire. 🔥

From being a foster kid to an NFL athlete to going through 30+traumatic experiences to a successful serial entrepreneur, he has seen it all.

And now he has weaved together psychology, neuroscience and life lessons into a powerful concept called the 𝐒𝐇𝐈𝐅𝐓 𝐌𝐄𝐓𝐇𝐎𝐃.

By Applying the Shift Method, you can unleash your true potential and achieve success in life. 🔝
